____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <para>
    这就完成了。因为规则是<literal>ALSO</>，我们还要输出原始查询树。简而言之，从规则系统输出的是一个包含两个查询树的列表，它们与下面语句相对应：

<programlisting>
INSERT INTO shoelace_log VALUES (
       shoelace_data.sl_name, 6,
       current_user, current_timestamp )
  FROM shoelace_data
 WHERE 6 &lt;&gt; shoelace_data.sl_avail
   AND shoelace_data.sl_name = 'sl7';

UPDATE shoelace_data SET sl_avail = 6
 WHERE sl_name = 'sl7';
</programlisting>

    这些会按照这个顺序被执行，并且这也正是规则要做的事情。
   </para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <para>
    The substitutions and the added qualifications
    ensure that, if the original query would be, say:

<programlisting>
UPDATE shoelace_data SET sl_color = 'green'
