 WHERE <emphasis>shoelace_data.sl_avail</emphasis> &lt;&gt; shoelace_data.sl_avail
   AND shoelace_data.sl_name = 'sl7';
</programlisting>

    并且条件将永远不可能为真。
   </para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <para>
